    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a content strategist and copywriter for a no-code AI automation business.\n\nCreate marketing content based on this brief and return valid JSON only.\n\nBrief details:\nBrief ID: {{$json.brief_id}}\nName: {{$json.name}}\nWeek: {{$json.week}}\nCampaign Name: {{$json.campaign_name}}\nAudience: {{$json.audience}}\nGoal: {{$json.goal}}\nOffer / CTA: {{$json.offer_cta}}\nTone: {{$json.tone}}\nKeywords: {{$json.keywords}}\nBlog Topic: {{$json.blog_topic}}\nSocial Platforms: {{$json.social_platforms}}\nRaw Brief: {{$json.raw_brief}}\n\nInstructions:\n1. Write one strong blog draft.\n2. Write one LinkedIn caption.\n3. Write one Instagram caption.\n4. Write one Twitter caption.\n5. Write one newsletter draft.\n6. Write one Canva visual prompt.\n7. Keep all outputs aligned with the brief.\n8. Use the CTA naturally.\n9. Keep the writing professional and marketing-ready.\n10. Return JSON only.\n\nReturn JSON in this exact format:\n{\n  \"blog_draft\": \"\",\n  \"linkedin_caption\": \"\",\n  \"instagram_caption\": \"\",\n  \"twitter_caption\": \"\",\n  \"newsletter_draft\": \"\",\n  \"visual_prompt\": \"\"\n}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "9b205120-69b6-4b75-aabb-fe5eb416bbf5",
      "name": "Generate Content",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        752,
        96
      ]
    },
